				<h1></h1>
				<p>Surprise your loved ones with a unique wine tasting trip, weekend or day.</p>

<p>Offer one of our wine tasting breaks with an open departure date. If you prefer, we can also design the wine tasting experience you want to offer.</p>

<p>Want to give them the choice? We will offer you a gift voucher from the value of your choice. The recipient of the gift will then choose one of our wine tasting breaks or a tailor made experience.</p>

<p>Check out these wine breaks to give you an idea of what we can offer:<br /><img src="squelettes-dist/puce.gif" width="8" height="11" class="puce" alt="-" />&nbsp;<b><a href="http://www.bleuvins.com/Tree-house-and-wine-discoveries.html" class='spip_out'>Tree house and wine break</a></b> <br /><img src="squelettes-dist/puce.gif" width="8" height="11" class="puce" alt="-" />&nbsp;<a href="http://www.bleuvins.com/Cave-dwelling-and-wines.html" class='spip_out'><b>Cave dwelling and wines</b></a><br /><img src="squelettes-dist/puce.gif" width="8" height="11" class="puce" alt="-" />&nbsp;<a href="http://www.bleuvins.com/Bordeaux-Saint-Emilion-Grands-Crus-156.html" class='spip_out'><b>Bordeaux &amp; Saint Emilion Grands Crus</b></a><br class='autobr' />
If you prefer, we can also design the wine tasting experience you want to offer.</p>

<p>Please contact us for further information on: +33 241 446 297 or by email <a href="mailto:contact@bleuvins.com"><u>contact@bleuvins.com</u></a></p>
